Package it.polimi.ingsw.messages.fromClient

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ActivateLeaderCardMessage
    contains leader cards' arraylist's index to activate a leader card.
    ActivatePersonalProductionMessage
    contains information about: 1) the two resources the user wants as production input.
    ActivateProductionMessage
    Invoked to activate productions.
    AskStartGameMessage
    Sent from a client if in waiting room there are less than 4 players.
    BuyDevCardMessage
    Sent from the client to buy specified development card.
    CalamaioResponseMessage
    message sent by the client TO THE SERVER, in response of the initialiseCalamaio message it contains the choice/s of te resources that a player will chose in the case he can.
    ClientMessage
    messages sent from client TO SERVER.
    ClientMessageFactory
    message factory USED BY the SERVER, to get a ClientMessage from a Json string.
    ClientPingMessage
    Test class used to ping the server.
    DiscardLeaderCardMessage
    Sent from the client to discard a leader card.
    EmptyMessage
    EmptyMessage doesn't do anything
    ExitFromGameMessage
    ExitFromGameMessage is used to send a message to the server and remove the clientHandler from the server.
    InsertResourcesInWarehouseMessage
    sent from the client and specifies warehouse shelf to insert resources contained in resources ArrayList.
    LoginMessage
    sent from the client to authenticate the user in the game.
    MoveWarehouseResourcesMessage
    Message sent from the client to move resources in warehouse between shelves.
    PickResourcesMessage
    Message sent from the user after the action "pick resources from market" has been selected.
    SelectLeaderCardMessage
    Message sent from the user to select two leader cards out of four at the beginning of the game.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    ClientMessageType
    messages that the client sends
